{"tid":2312431,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"聖誕送咩禮物","createTime":"2020-12-05T02:55:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T08:23:46.000Z","uid":207977,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b819e4f13f4598d7067883613be38634fbbc4d03","tid":2312431,"uid":207977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T02:55:06.000Z","msg":"聖誕又準備到啦<br />\n<br />\n本身我諗住比個驚喜佢，<br />\n買iphone12pro做聖誕禮物<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為知佢電話壞壞地，同佢想要嘅野我又買唔起(車，名錶個類）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但電話依d我仲負擔得到，所以就揀電話。<br />\n點知佢部電話琴日壞到佢話今日想去買<br />\n心諗: Shit! 佢自己買咁我送咩好....手機生性d捱到25號先壞啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我拖緊佢唔好買機住，但唔係辦法都要諗定plan b<br />\n大家諗定送咩比另一伴未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n叔叔通常鍾意d咩？<br />\n想參考下"},{"pid":"871fe3138375bd5270c81ca780abcd1252f309b0","tid":2312431,"uid":65116,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T02:56:27.000Z","msg":"提早送佢比囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1036a48288ca3e4397a32c2be0db86522e1b3d72","tid":2312431,"uid":207977,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"871fe3138375bd5270c81ca780abcd1252f309b0","tid":2312431,"uid":65116,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T02:56:27.000Z","msg":"提早送佢比囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T02:58:46.000Z","msg":"但想正日送<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"065cc782fb9dc03fdb0846e0eb61308ab1a7d85c","tid":2312431,"uid":65116,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"1036a48288ca3e4397a32c2be0db86522e1b3d72","tid":2312431,"uid":207977,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"871fe3138375bd5270c81ca780abcd1252f309b0","tid":2312431,"uid":65116,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T02:56